Package: cutpointr
Type: Package
Title: Determine and evaluate optimal cutpoints in binary
    classification tasks
Version: 0.2.2
Authors@R: person("Christian", "Thiele", email = "c.thiele@hs-osnabrueck.de",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: In addition to finding the cutpoint that maximizes a chosen metric
    the package includes functions for bootstrapping and validating cutpoints.
